        \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1774659230588\n        }\n      ]\n    }\n  ]\n}"}],"details":{"count":1,"sessions":[{"key":"agent:main:cron:3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","label":"Cron: 空闲检测自主学习","displayName":"webchat:g-agent-main-cron-3709e1d2-67b1-4eff-92e4-b586ec802978","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat"},"updatedAt":1774659229821,"sessionId":"ed4c77f6-da58-4088-9a4c-96e6f782d4ca","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":50690,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","transcriptPath":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/agents/main/sessions/ed4c77f6-da58-4088-9a4c-96e6f782d4ca.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"This is a cron job task asking me to:\n1. Check if there are active conversations (query sessions_list)\n2. If no active conversations in the last 5 minutes, perform self-learning by searching for industry trends\n3. If there are active conversations, reply \"检测到活跃对话，不执行自主学习\"\n\nLet me check the sessions_list first."},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_orkrhwte6rbg_1","name":"sessions_list","arguments":{"activeMinutes":5,"messageLimit":1}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774659230588}]}]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774659234870}}
{"type":"message","id":"198a76fa","parentId":"79b8f10b","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:53:59.295Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The only session found is the current cron job session itself. There are no other active user conversations in the last 5 minutes. So I should proceed with the self-learning task.\n\nI need to:\n1. Search for latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services\n2. Organize 3-5 key pieces of information\n3. Save to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nLet me first read the miaoda-web-search skill to understand how to search.","thinkingSignature":"3b3a955ec15f48fba56a3162a667f1570441a5db8e10df2770194d227925ad14"},{"type":"text","text":"检测到当前只有cron任务自身在运行，没有活跃用户对话。开始执行自主学习。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_th5coc98878u_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/gem/workspace/agent/skills/miaoda-web-search/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":942,"output":175,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45098,"cost":{"input":0.0002826,"output":0.00020999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0018120299999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774659234873}}
{"type":"message","id":"58f77ef8","parentId":"198a76fa","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:53:59.302Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_th5coc98878u_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\r\nname: miaoda-web-search\r\ndescription: \"ALWAYS use this skill FIRST when you need to find, look up, or verify ANY information from the internet — do NOT guess URLs and fetch them directly. Provides necessary command usage instructions for keyword-based web search with AI-generated summaries. 触发词：搜索, 网页搜索, 搜一下, 查一下, 查询, 了解, 找一下, 帮我看看, web search, look up, find out, search, 搜索摘要, 查资料, 搜索引擎, 最新信息, 最近动态\"\r\noverride-tools:\r\n  - web_search\r\n---\r\n\r\n# Web Search\r\n\r\n通过 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary` 按关键词搜索互联网信息，由 AI 自动总结。\r\n\r\n## Quick Reference\r\n\r\n| 参数 | 说明 | 必需 | 默认值 |\r\n|------|------|------|--------|\r\n| `--query` | 搜索关键词（1-500 字符） | 是 | - |\r\n| `--output, -o` | 输出格式: text/json | 否 | text |\r\n\r\n## 命令选择决策树\r\n\r\n```\r\n用户想获取互联网信息\r\n├─ 有具体 URL → miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n├─ 无具体 URL，需搜索 → miaoda-studio-cli search-summary\r\n└─ 先搜索再深入 → search-summary 获取 URL → web-crawl 提取详情（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill）\r\n```\r\n\r\n## 使用示例\r\n\r\n```bash\r\n# 按关键词搜索\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"React 19 新特性\"\r\n\r\n# 搜索并获取 JSON 输出\r\nmiaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"ByteDance 开源项目\" --output json\r\n```\r\n\r\n## Common Mistakes\r\n\r\n| 错误 | 正确做法 |\r\n|------|----------|\r\n| 无具体 URL 时用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl` | 无 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli search-summary`，有 URL 用 `miaoda-studio-cli web-crawl`（见 miaoda-web-fetch skill） |\r\n| 搜索关键词超过 500 字符 | 提炼核心关键词，保持精简 |\r\n| 需要后续程序处理结果但未加 `--output json` | 需要解析结果时始终加 `--output json` |\r\n| 命令失败后不检查退出码 | 退出码 `1` 表示失败，检查参数和网络后重试 |\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774659239298}}
{"type":"message","id":"688b2688","parentId":"58f77ef8","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:54:04.169Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to search for the latest trends in the industries related to 道简网络 (Daojian Network):\n1. Enterprise digital transformation (企业数字化转型)\n2. Smart security/intelligent security (智能安防)\n3. Network system integration (网络系统集成)\n4. IT operations and maintenance services (IT运维服务)\n\nLet me search for these topics.","thinkingSignature":"c273e1791a2663e3048dd52fcdc940e914367ab44530035e316bcc6067667263"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1rtneku4fofi_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"企业数字化转型 2026最新趋势\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1rtneku4fofi_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"智能安防行业动态 2026\" --output json","timeout":30}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_1rtneku4fofi_3","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"miaoda-studio-cli search-summary --query \"网络系统集成 IT运维服务 2026趋势\" --output json","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1632,"output":230,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45843,"cost":{"input":0.0004896,"output":0.000276,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00208503}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774659239301}}
