{"type":"message","id":"10d08dfb","parentId":"19839ba0","timestamp":"2026-03-28T00:55:13.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I've completed the self-learning task. The cron job was triggered, there were no active user conversations in the last 5 minutes, so I:\n1. Searched for latest trends in enterprise digital transformation, smart security, network system integration, and IT operations services\n2. Organized 5 key pieces of information covering these 4 areas\n3. Saved to /home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md\n\nThe task is complete.","thinkingSignature":"c241531209609d8f2a25b18623a6bd847acd77588f66ecd36f1412c847b2775a"},{"type":"text","text":"已完成自主学习任务。\n\n**执行情况**：\n- ✅ 无活跃对话（当前仅有cron任务自身运行）\n- ✅ 搜索了企业数字化转型、智能安防、网络系统集成、IT运维服务等4个领域的最新动态\n- ✅ 整理了5个关键信息模块\n- ✅ 已保存至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`\n\n**本次学习要点**：\n1. **AI智能体**成为企业数字化核心驱动力，多智能体协作生态兴起\n2. **智能安防**从\"事后追溯\"转向\"事中预警\"，大模型+具身智能是方向\n3. **AIOps向Agentic AIOps**演进，动态CMDB+知识图谱构建IT\"活地图\"\n4. **网络安全合规**要求升级（等保三级、数据脱敏成为标配）\n5. **运维自动化**（DevOps融合、NLOps自然语言运维）是核心竞争力"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4981,"output":293,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49255,"cost":{"input":0.0014942999999999998,"output":0.0003516,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0031653299999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774659307268}}
